These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-1::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cycling, parkour, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
2. the person who's sport is cycling is on the far right##1
3. the person who's sport is cycling is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |       2       |   3   |
| Sport   | weightlifting | parkour | cycling |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-2::.
There 3 different types of food: orange, blueberry, pear
1. the person eating blueberry is in an odd position##4
2. the person eating orange is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |     2      |   3    |
| Food   | orange | pear | blueberry |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-3::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: sudoku, camping, singing
1. the person who's hobby is camping is in an even position##4
2. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is singing##3
3. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |      3       |
| Hobby   | sudoku | camping | singing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-4::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: indie, hip-hop, r&b
1. the fan of hip-hop is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of r&b is on the left of the fan of hip-hop##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |  3   |
| Music-Genre   | indie | r&b | hip-hop |

